            <h2>
              Module 1: Network Fundamentals
              <span class="badge">Foundation</span>
            </h2>
            <p>
              Core networking building blocks needed before moving to switching
              and routing configuration.
            </p>

            <table>
              <thead>
              <tr>
                <th style="width:25%;">Module</th>
